fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "hotdoc_markdown/gtktooltip.html#gtk_tooltip_set_tip_area", "fragment": "gtk_tooltip_set_tip_area \nGtk.prototype.set_tip_area \nGtk.Tooltip.set_tip_area \nSets the area of the widget where the contents of this tooltip apply to be rect in widget coordinates This is especially useful for properly setting tooltips on GtkTreeView rows and cells GtkIconView etc. \nFor setting tooltips on GtkTreeView please refer to the convenience functions for this gtk_tree_view_set_tooltip_row and gtk_tree_view_set_tooltip_cell. \nParameters \na GtkTooltip \na GdkRectangle \nSince \nSets the area of the widget where the contents of this tooltip apply to be rect in widget coordinates This is especially useful for properly setting tooltips on Gtk.TreeView rows and cells Gtk.IconView etc. \nFor setting tooltips on Gtk.TreeView please refer to the convenience functions for this Gtk.prototype.set_tooltip_row and Gtk.prototype.set_tooltip_cell. \nParameters \na Gtk.Tooltip \na Gdk.Rectangle \nSince \nSets the area of the widget where the contents of this tooltip apply to be rect in widget coordinates This is especially useful for properly setting tooltips on Gtk.TreeView rows and cells Gtk.IconView etc. \nFor setting tooltips on Gtk.TreeView please refer to the convenience functions for this Gtk.TreeView.set_tooltip_row and Gtk.TreeView.set_tooltip_cell. \nParameters \na Gtk.Tooltip \na Gdk.Rectangle \nSince \n"});